#  Cardiac Arrest Rare Among Marathoners, Study Finds

![Heart Marathoners](http://i.huffpost.com/gen/463503/thumbs/r-HEART-
MARATHONERS-large570.jpg)

By MALCOLM RITTER   01/11/12 05:16 PM ET   Associated
Press![AP](http://s.huffpost.com/images/v/ap_wire.png)

React

![](/images/bignews/follow-arrow.png)

