![](/images/bignews/follow-arrow.png)

  Video  ,  Heart Incidents Marathoners  ,  Heart Marathoners  ,  Heart Risk
Marathoners  ,  Marathon Runners Heart  ,  Marathoners Health  ,  Runners
Heart  ,  Runners Heart Incidents  ,  Runners Heart Risks  ,  Healthy Living
News

#### share this story

Get Healthy Living Alerts

